WEBVTT

00:00:15.397 --> 00:00:19.897
UNK

00:00:19.987 --> 00:00:22.102
UNK

00:00:22.102 --> 00:00:23.661
KHATSKEL ZAK.

00:00:24.932 --> 00:00:28.321
EH UNK KHAIM BARGMAN.

00:00:28.357 --> 00:00:32.254
UNK YIDISH.

00:00:39.242 --> 00:00:40.437
haynt iz der

00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:42.459
fir un tsvontsikster merts,

00:00:42.583 --> 00:00:45.446
toyznt nayn hundert zeks un nayntsiktn yor.

00:00:45.789 --> 00:00:47.373
der intervyu vet gebn

00:00:47.373 --> 00:00:48.838
Khatzkel Zak.

00:00:49.822 --> 00:00:51.532
Lite, Kovne.

00:00:51.560 --> 00:00:53.135
di intervyu vet nemen

00:00:53.135 --> 00:00:54.862
Khaim Bargman.

00:01:04.976 --> 00:01:06.658
ikh bin geboyrn gevorn

00:01:07.288 --> 00:01:12.649
in toyznt nayn hundert akht un tsvontsikstn yor, in finf un tsvontsikstn may.

00:01:16.113 --> 00:01:18.623
in a shtetele Shokyan,

00:01:24.095 --> 00:01:25.254
a ⟨landverk⟩.

00:01:26.913 --> 00:01:29.456
mayn foter hot farmogt finf un fertsik akern,

00:01:29.698 --> 00:01:32.156
un me iz geven akht brider un a shvester.

00:01:35.672 --> 00:01:39.446
zogt undz bite, vu gefint zikh der shtetl Shokyan?

00:01:40.413 --> 00:01:43.394
der shtetl Shkoyan gefint zikh tsvishn Kelm un ⟨Shavl⟩.

00:01:43.805 --> 00:01:47.512
vifl umgefer kilometer iz fun Shokyan biz Shavl?

00:01:47.231 --> 00:01:48.710
eyn un draysik kilometer.

00:01:51.062 --> 00:01:53.183
dertseylt vayter yo, es,

00:01:55.567 --> 00:01:58.008
az mir zaynen geven akht kinder, akht brider,

00:01:59.347 --> 00:02:01.029
un yene tsayt iz geven

00:02:01.288 --> 00:02:02.947
in shtetl iz nit geven keyn

00:02:02.947 --> 00:02:04.269
hebreishn lerer,

00:02:06.536 --> 00:02:09.199
hot mayn foter gehatn a lererin bay zikh

00:02:09.199 --> 00:02:09.989
in shtub.

00:02:11.278 --> 00:02:14.023
un ayer foter aleyn hot gekent redn hebreish?

00:02:13.742 --> 00:02:14.428
yo.

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.216
vu hot er zikh gelernt?

00:02:16.965 --> 00:02:18.461
mayn foter hot zikh gelernt

00:02:18.602 --> 00:02:21.971
in in di amolike yeshives hot er zikh gelernt, a mol.

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:24.367
in yeshive, a mol a mol a mol.

00:02:24.103 --> 00:02:26.848
in vos far a yeshive hot zikh gelernt ayer foter?

00:02:25.942 --> 00:02:26.848
in Kelm.

00:02:27.123 --> 00:02:28.923
in Kelm iz geven a yeshive?

00:02:28.518 --> 00:02:28.968
yo.

00:02:28.997 --> 00:02:31.675
efsher gedenkt ir vi iz geven der nomen fun der yeshive?

00:02:31.292 --> 00:02:32.586
dos ken ikh aykh nit zogn.

00:02:33.907 --> 00:02:37.259
un ayer, ayer muter iz geven a gebildete froy?

00:02:37.383 --> 00:02:39.942
neyn, mayn muter iz nit geven keyn gebildete, nor zi hot gekent

00:02:40.050 --> 00:02:44.145
i der shraybn un leyenen hot zi gekent altsding gut, bentshn likht un

00:02:45.028 --> 00:02:46.131
makhn dos

00:02:46.131 --> 00:02:47.841
oyf shabes tsugreytn altsding

00:02:48.048 --> 00:02:50.540
yontevdik, oyf yontoyvim,

00:02:51.660 --> 00:02:54.202
un undz lernen vi tsu makhn di brokhes

00:02:55.727 --> 00:02:56.804
farn esn.

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:58.589
nokhn esn, farn shlofn,

00:02:59.307 --> 00:03:01.897
un me zogt in der fri, un altsding.

00:03:02.375 --> 00:03:06.571
ayer muter hot aykh nisht dertseylt vu hot ir zikh gelernt yidish, shraybn leyenen?

00:03:06.425 --> 00:03:07.381
mayn muter?

00:03:07.100 --> 00:03:08.984
yo. ver hot ir gelernt?

00:03:07.674 --> 00:03:09.744
in in shtetl Gruzt.

00:03:10.357 --> 00:03:12.202
dos iz dos iz

00:03:12.247 --> 00:03:15.026
zekhtsn kilometer fun Savl.

00:03:15.487 --> 00:03:17.017
un ver hot ir gelernt?

00:03:18.103 --> 00:03:22.349
oykh amolike gelernte yidn, heyst es in di shtetlekh hobn zey gelernt.

00:03:22.524 --> 00:03:23.818
shtetisher lerer.

00:03:23.418 --> 00:03:24.627
shtetisher lerer.

00:03:24.853 --> 00:03:27.466
un ayer foter hot gekent redn rusish,

00:03:27.466 --> 00:03:28.458
litvish?

00:03:27.468 --> 00:03:28.188
yo.

00:03:29.105 --> 00:03:30.331
un geleyent?

00:03:31.350 --> 00:03:35.411
yo er hot gekent rusish, un litvish, un un un un un afile poylish.

00:03:35.872 --> 00:03:40.726
un velkhn shtot felgt arayngeyn a tsaytung, vos far a tsaytung iz dos geven?

00:03:43.500 --> 00:03:47.392
yene yorn iz keyn tsaytung in di shtetlekh nisht kimat UNK geven.

00:03:48.950 --> 00:03:51.391
der gantser tsaytung iz geven der geyn in shul.

00:03:52.595 --> 00:03:53.737
dray mol a tog.

00:03:53.878 --> 00:03:55.982
mayn foter flegt geyn in shul dray mol a tog.

00:03:56.240 --> 00:04:00.706
ver nit iz fun ayer mishpokhe, ayere brider, flegn bagleytn der, ayer foter?

00:04:02.923 --> 00:04:04.329
nu!

00:04:04.329 --> 00:04:05.381
ir farshteyt,

00:04:05.842 --> 00:04:09.785
ikh vel aykh veln zogn eyn zakh, az ikh bin geblibn on foter bin ikh geven fir yor alt.

00:04:12.592 --> 00:04:13.788
nor az mayn foter

00:04:13.788 --> 00:04:16.890
hot mayne brider gelernt ivrit,

00:04:17.468 --> 00:04:18.829
hot men gedungen a lerer.

00:04:19.021 --> 00:04:20.602
un ikh gedenk

00:04:20.996 --> 00:04:22.290
zeyer gut, gedenk ikh.

00:04:22.616 --> 00:04:24.129
az mayn mame flegt zogn,

00:04:25.299 --> 00:04:26.216
"kinder!

00:04:26.244 --> 00:04:30.165
ir muzt zikh gut lernen ivrit, kenen gut ivrit un lernen!

00:04:30.176 --> 00:04:32.668
vayl es kumen, zogt er, a tsayt, ven nit iz,

00:04:33.095 --> 00:04:36.872
vos ir vet darfn zikh derzogn kadesh, ir vet zikh arayngeyn in shul,

00:04:36.875 --> 00:04:38.712
ir vet darfn zikh trefn mit mentshn.

00:04:38.712 --> 00:04:42.686
dos vet forkumen, zogt er, aza min tsayt vet vern." un mayn fa- un mayn mame

00:04:42.686 --> 00:04:44.092
hot dos take rikhtik gezogt.

00:04:44.942 --> 00:04:46.472
zi flegt zikh betn bay mir,

00:04:47.085 --> 00:04:49.492
vayl ikh, vos ikh hob zikh gelernt in kheyder,

00:04:51.033 --> 00:04:52.529
nokh demolts BEFORE di krig,

00:04:54.257 --> 00:04:55.787
iz geven shvere tsaytn.

00:04:56.282 --> 00:04:57.728
undz zenen geblibn on foter,

00:04:58.745 --> 00:04:59.684
ir farshteyt?

00:04:59.977 --> 00:05:03.448
di erd nit ale yor flegn gebn ire,

00:05:04.230 --> 00:05:06.519
vos vet darfn, vi heyst es, oysvaksn ire.

00:05:06.660 --> 00:05:09.236
geven alerleyke yorn, shlekhte un besere yorn.

00:05:09.815 --> 00:05:11.683
un azoy vi bay undz flegt zayn

00:05:12.482 --> 00:05:14.467
sahbesdike teg, shabes

00:05:15.148 --> 00:05:15.989
flegn mir zikh

00:05:15.989 --> 00:05:17.184
tsu keyn zakh nit tsurirn.

00:05:17.325 --> 00:05:19.378
flegt men darfn dingen mentshn,

00:05:20.413 --> 00:05:22.722
nu lomir zogn litviner, oder di

00:05:22.722 --> 00:05:26.266
gevezen rusn, zey flegn lozn flegn shabes muzn

00:05:26.266 --> 00:05:28.291
ton ale arbet far di beheymes,

00:05:28.291 --> 00:05:30.077
beheymes iz nit geven nit veynik,

00:05:30.285 --> 00:05:31.531
mir ho'mir gehat tsvelf ki,

00:05:31.533 --> 00:05:32.422
un ferd,

00:05:32.985 --> 00:05:35.679
a draysik shepsn, un oyfes un

00:05:36.056 --> 00:05:37.741
veyst dikh vi a gev- vi a

00:05:37.743 --> 00:05:38.736
vi a virtshaft,

00:05:38.736 --> 00:05:39.831
vos geyt for dort.

00:05:44.460 --> 00:05:45.214
nu!

00:05:45.405 --> 00:05:46.851
eyn zakh vel ikh aykh zogn,

00:05:48.543 --> 00:05:53.820
az mir zaynen geven tsu fil ayngelozn zikh in in

00:05:54.399 --> 00:05:57.498
in di toyre, vi me zogt in yidishkeyt. tsu fil.

00:05:59.225 --> 00:06:03.691
der umglik mit mayn foter hot pasirt er iz krank mitn apenditsit fraytik tsu nakht.

00:06:05.385 --> 00:06:07.657
un fraytik tsu nakht men tor nisht arbetn.

00:06:08.507 --> 00:06:14.258
dos zaynen draysik kilomoter, amolike tsaytn mit di mit di ferdn, di vegn geven zeyer shlekhte, durkh di velder.

00:06:14.258 --> 00:06:15.777
mit hobn gelebt tsvishn velder un

00:06:15.797 --> 00:06:19.431
zamd, di ferdn flegn nit kenen aroysgeyn shver.

00:06:19.431 --> 00:06:24.324
un trots dem hot er gezogt, ikh zol beser do shtarbn in shtub

00:06:24.324 --> 00:06:25.882
nor shabes vel ikh nit forn.

00:06:26.833 --> 00:06:28.785
un di brider hobn gezogt, "tate!

00:06:29.077 --> 00:06:30.762
in di toyre iz dokh ongeshribn

00:06:30.762 --> 00:06:32.193
az a yid very krank,

00:06:32.790 --> 00:06:35.569
afile a rov, shabes,

00:06:35.625 --> 00:06:36.834
un es drot im

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:38.099
der lebn,

00:06:38.612 --> 00:06:40.277
hobn mir dokh oykh dos tsu ton."

00:06:40.738 --> 00:06:43.686
zogt er, "ki- kinder," zogt er, "ikh hob aykh ale mayn holts,

00:06:44.501 --> 00:06:46.200
ober shabes vel ikh nit forn."

00:06:48.146 --> 00:06:49.541
hot er gevart biz

00:06:51.048 --> 00:06:52.274
shabes far nakht,

00:06:52.415 --> 00:06:53.945
un UNK shabes far nakht,

00:06:56.212 --> 00:07:01.117
ikh bin geven a yingl UNK iber fir yor, gedenk nokh bizn hayntikn tog, er hot zikh mit undz alemen gezegnt,

00:07:02.777 --> 00:07:05.252
mit ale kinder hot er zikh gezegnt, mit mayne tsvey brider,

00:07:05.578 --> 00:07:07.412
mit di shvester hobn im bagleyt,

00:07:07.957 --> 00:07:08.846
biz Savl.

00:07:10.472 --> 00:07:18.364
un er iz gekumen shoyn in Savl, hot er zikh gefilt zeyer shlekht, UNK forndik shlekhte vegn hot im geplatst.

00:07:20.141 --> 00:07:22.582
hot im aroysgenumen a profesor fun Kenigsberg

00:07:25.406 --> 00:07:27.274
un er hot im nit gekent rateven.

00:07:27.870 --> 00:07:30.598
un damolt yene yorn hot men im batsolt dray tsoyznt lit,

00:07:32.207 --> 00:07:33.501
dos iz geven groyse gelt,

00:07:34.940 --> 00:07:36.149
un mir zaynen geblibn

00:07:37.404 --> 00:07:38.698
yesoymim, vo me zogt.

00:07:39.918 --> 00:07:40.959
nor er

00:07:41.910 --> 00:07:43.508
in, nokh zayendik in

00:07:44.812 --> 00:07:46.629
in kranknhoyz in Savl,

00:07:47.343 --> 00:07:49.346
hot er dem eltern bruder ongezogt,

00:07:51.191 --> 00:07:54.257
zogt er, "mayn tayere zun," zogt er,

00:08:01.400 --> 00:08:02.289
UNK

00:08:04.151 --> 00:08:07.115
"zolst zayn," zogt er, "a foter far dayne kinder, far di far di far,

00:08:08.370 --> 00:08:10.710
far di klenere kinder, zey oyshodeven,

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:12.448
UNK," zogt er, "lernen zikh,

00:08:13.145 --> 00:08:14.675
oyb zey zoln nor veln," zogt er,

00:08:15.272 --> 00:08:16.465
"fun di letste,"

00:08:19.288 --> 00:08:20.615
un er iz geshtorbn.

00:08:22.005 --> 00:08:23.822
az mayn foter iz geshtorbn

00:08:25.177 --> 00:08:26.471
hob ikh mir a briv do.

00:08:26.544 --> 00:08:29.188
un gedankt di sh- zayne shvester vos hot gelebt in Afrike.

00:08:30.813 --> 00:08:33.170
mayn foter iz geven zeyer a groyser a klal tuer.

00:08:34.644 --> 00:08:37.085
er flegt ale yorn oyf yontoyvim

00:08:38.306 --> 00:08:39.450
tsvey furn,

00:08:39.450 --> 00:08:41.050
eyns barn tsveyte oyf ferd,

00:08:42.221 --> 00:08:43.397
un brengen

00:08:43.469 --> 00:08:45.827
gemolene, vayse veytsene mel,

00:08:46.794 --> 00:08:47.700
mit ⟨pulves⟩,

00:08:48.735 --> 00:08:51.041
oyb es vet zayn a kalb, a geborene,

00:08:52.059 --> 00:08:56.643
un a tsvey kelber, mit a sheps, lebedike, mit oyfes, far oreme yidn in shtetl.

00:09:00.598 --> 00:09:02.434
dos hot nokh her

00:09:02.437 --> 00:09:03.849
Abe Sholem Dirge,

00:09:04.108 --> 00:09:05.284
vos hot gelebt do.

00:09:05.424 --> 00:09:06.262
Hershl.

00:09:06.960 --> 00:09:11.477
zayne fraynt hobn gelebt bay mir in UNK, flegt er kumen, flegt er dos dermonen alts in shul far ale yidn,

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:13.133
ver mayn foter iz geven un mayn

00:09:13.133 --> 00:09:15.454
tantes hobn geshikt di briv vos zey hobn mir gebetn,

00:09:15.454 --> 00:09:16.353
"Khatskele,

00:09:17.304 --> 00:09:19.863
du zolst zayn azane," zogt zi, "punkt der foter iz geven.

00:09:20.274 --> 00:09:21.736
zolst helfn mentshn."

00:09:24.206 --> 00:09:24.993
nu!

00:09:25.185 --> 00:09:29.111
mir zaynen geblibn zelbe UNK, veyst dokh UNK vifl me hot gekent,

00:09:30.534 --> 00:09:31.861
biz arum di milkhome.

00:09:33.335 --> 00:09:36.198
vifl yor iz geven ayere elterer bruder

00:09:36.288 --> 00:09:38.054
ven iz geshtorbn ayer foter?

00:09:38.280 --> 00:09:41.582
mayn elterer bruder iz geven UNK der foter iz er shoyn gevezn,

00:09:42.903 --> 00:09:45.074
in zekhtstn yor iz er geven dos iz,

00:09:46.548 --> 00:09:49.211
un der foter iz geshtorbn in dray un draysikstn.

00:09:51.678 --> 00:09:52.432
un dos,

00:09:53.366 --> 00:09:54.694
nor zibetsn yor?

00:09:55.408 --> 00:09:57.090
UNK iz geven akhtsn yor.

00:09:56.994 --> 00:10:00.633
un oyf im iz es dan gelign di gantse last fun virtshaft.

00:10:00.791 --> 00:10:01.427
yo.

00:10:01.179 --> 00:10:02.540
un oyf ayer muter.

00:10:01.635 --> 00:10:03.199
mit di mamen, mit di mamen, yo.

00:10:04.875 --> 00:10:08.227
dertseylt epes vi hot ir zkh ongehoybn lernen

00:10:08.756 --> 00:10:10.050
in ayer shtetl?

00:10:12.924 --> 00:10:14.302
mir hobn zikh gelernt

00:10:14.561 --> 00:10:15.402
tsum ersht

00:10:15.422 --> 00:10:17.216
hob ikh dertseylt, undz ho'mir gehaltn a

00:10:17.227 --> 00:10:19.115
a eltern mentshn, a lerer.

00:10:19.115 --> 00:10:24.427
a UNK a elterer mentsh. a oreme yid, ober a gelernter, hot er gekent sh- er hot gekent dos ⟨verter⟩ oyf

00:10:24.500 --> 00:10:25.811
di shvartse pintlekh.

00:10:25.985 --> 00:10:27.448
flegt men undz lernen in sh-

00:10:27.993 --> 00:10:28.747
in shtub.

00:10:29.175 --> 00:10:31.194
UNK er bay undz shlofn un esn

00:10:32.111 --> 00:10:37.522
un batsoln flegt men ⟨bilik, flegt er betn⟩ im er iz geven gut az er hot gehat vu tsum shlofn, un tsum esn.

00:10:37.882 --> 00:10:39.007
un mir hobn gehat

00:10:40.127 --> 00:10:41.387
UNK kleyne shtub

00:10:42.658 --> 00:10:43.935
nit vayt fun shtetl.

00:10:44.750 --> 00:10:49.267
in shtetl hot men dokh nit UNK, lebn shtetl, dray kilometer fun shtetl.

00:10:50.657 --> 00:10:52.761
nokh dem az mir hobn shoyn gekent merer,

00:10:54.437 --> 00:10:55.579
me un me geyt in,

00:10:56.057 --> 00:10:57.013
in klas,

00:10:57.407 --> 00:10:58.330
in shtetl.

00:10:59.347 --> 00:11:00.939
ober keyn ⟨registrirter⟩

00:11:00.939 --> 00:11:03.679
lerers in di yene tsaytn iz nokh nit geven.

00:11:06.114 --> 00:11:08.488
a, flegn mir hobn UNK

00:11:08.544 --> 00:11:09.534
oyf ivrit

00:11:10.856 --> 00:11:14.748
tsvey sho, oyf yidish tsvey sho, un a tsvey sho litvish.

00:11:15.176 --> 00:11:19.001
ot az ikh hob shoyn ongefangen un ts- ikh bin geven in tsveytn klas,

00:11:19.445 --> 00:11:21.105
iz shoyn geven registrirter

00:11:21.105 --> 00:11:21.907
lerers.

00:11:21.907 --> 00:11:22.851
flegn mir der bokher

00:11:22.851 --> 00:11:24.519
hot shoyn ongefangen geyn tsoln gehalt.

00:11:24.980 --> 00:11:26.291
un rekhenen?

00:11:26.702 --> 00:11:27.911
matematika?

00:11:29.199 --> 00:11:32.602
nu di zelbe, registrirte lerers, zey hobn shoyn gekent altsding dos.

00:11:38.126 --> 00:11:41.006
mayn lererke, hob ikh do oyfn bild fun for di krig.

00:11:42.767 --> 00:11:45.124
vi iz geven di nomen fun ayer lererke?

00:11:44.876 --> 00:11:45.987
Khane Yudeykin.

00:11:45.987 --> 00:11:46.845
fun ⟨Zaga⟩.

00:11:46.766 --> 00:11:49.376
un zi hot gekent say yidish, say hebreish?

00:11:48.977 --> 00:11:51.351
zi hot gekent yidish un litvish.

00:11:51.727 --> 00:11:53.713
un hebreish hot gelernt an ander lerer.

00:11:54.444 --> 00:11:56.598
un a lerer oyf tanakh hot ir gehat?

00:11:56.807 --> 00:11:57.409
yo.

00:11:57.650 --> 00:11:59.703
un der lerer oyf tanakh hot,

00:11:58.764 --> 00:12:01.880
Hershl, Hershl ⟨Paklibak⟩ der ler- der rov.

00:12:02.477 --> 00:12:06.015
der ah der der shtetlesher rov hot aykh gelernt tanakh?

00:12:06.290 --> 00:12:07.398
se geven tsvey rabonim.

00:12:07.505 --> 00:12:09.372
a elterer un a yingerer.

00:12:10.037 --> 00:12:10.706
i-

00:12:10.037 --> 00:12:11.921
der el- der yingerer hot men gedungen.

00:12:11.673 --> 00:12:13.541
un hebreish ver hot aykh gelernt?

00:12:13.226 --> 00:12:14.216
der zelber.

00:12:14.120 --> 00:12:15.245
der zelber rov.

00:12:14.508 --> 00:12:16.814
un farharn flegt kumen der alter rov.

00:12:19.098 --> 00:12:24.965
