00:24:07.646 --> 00:24:11.015
a umgefer a nayntsik meter, akhtsik meter fun di grub vi me hot geshosn.

00:24:11.190 --> 00:24:13.204
un zey hobn ale, ale shtetleshe,

00:24:13.204 --> 00:24:14.925
hobn zey gevust alemen's nemen,

00:24:14.953 --> 00:24:18.154
ver es iz gegangen, vemen hot geshisn, tsu ver es zenen gegangen, un altsding.

00:24:19.155 --> 00:24:22.153
un zey zenen geven a zeyer ongesh- shikere,

00:24:22.327 --> 00:24:26.087
zey hobn geshosn drotn, se vet pasirn az mit eyn

00:24:26.107 --> 00:24:28.650
nit getrofn, der koyl, hot men geshisn tsvey,

00:24:28.773 --> 00:24:31.062
in eyn mentshn, eyner in kop, eyner in hartsn.

00:24:31.440 --> 00:24:32.990
nor az me iz shiker UNK

00:24:32.990 --> 00:24:35.264
un arayngefaln mentshn

00:24:35.422 --> 00:24:36.226
in grub,

00:24:37.413 --> 00:24:40.212
andere UNK geshosn. andere flegn shisn zey hobn ge⟨UNK⟩

00:24:40.212 --> 00:24:41.627
fir mentshn eyn mentshn.

00:24:42.881 --> 00:24:44.919
dos hot pasirt mit mayn shvoger un dos

00:24:44.940 --> 00:24:46.305
oyfn bild hob ikh im do.

00:24:47.758 --> 00:24:54.199
