00:24:55.807 --> 00:24:58.988
nor zey hobn dershosn UNK.

00:24:58.372 --> 00:25:00.813
vifl zey zenen geven in tsol, di yidishe zayt?

00:25:02.220 --> 00:25:05.387
vi mir hobn gehert iz geven a hundert etlekhe un tsvontsik.

00:25:06.253 --> 00:25:08.340
hundert etlekhe un tsvontsik yidishe zayt?

00:25:07.991 --> 00:25:09.454
yo dortn in shtetl.

00:25:10.202 --> 00:25:12.511
nor ale zaynen gegangen shisn.

00:25:12.511 --> 00:25:14.165
a teyl iz gegangen shisn

00:25:14.165 --> 00:25:15.461
un a teyl hobn gerabirt,

00:25:15.737 --> 00:25:16.558
di zakhn,

00:25:17.610 --> 00:25:18.971
dos veys ikh hundert protsent.

00:25:21.339 --> 00:25:24.962
vos iz ge- farfolgn perzenlekh mit aykh?

00:25:25.068 --> 00:25:28.825
az ir zayt dokh, ir zayt dokh oykhet geven farmakht in dem zelbikn bud.

00:25:28.072 --> 00:25:30.598
aha, geven farmakht, ikh mit Kalmenen.

00:25:30.654 --> 00:25:31.796
UNK

00:25:32.105 --> 00:25:33.348
un nokh kinder.

00:25:35.430 --> 00:25:37.365
se hot zikh ayngegebn aza moment,

00:25:39.733 --> 00:25:41.380
ikh bin geven geranet

00:25:41.488 --> 00:25:42.658
in hant un,

00:25:41.842 --> 00:25:43.372
farvundet, yo?

00:25:42.658 --> 00:25:45.650
farvundet, yo, in hant in rukn, ober nit shtark.

00:25:46.719 --> 00:25:48.165
ven zent ir gelofn?

00:25:49.487 --> 00:25:50.730
se hot mir dershosn,

00:25:51.005 --> 00:25:52.909
haynt veys ikh voser UNK

00:25:52.909 --> 00:25:56.990
fun fun dem hoyf hot men geshi- alemen gefirt in di vald, dray kilometer in vald.

00:25:58.110 --> 00:25:59.724
iz ir zayt oykh gegangen.

00:25:59.460 --> 00:26:00.349
gegangen.

00:26:00.860 --> 00:26:01.850
me hot UNK gefirt.

00:26:03.476 --> 00:26:06.204
un ven hot ir bashlosn az ir darft loyfn?

00:26:08.505 --> 00:26:09.380
ir farshteyt,

00:26:09.416 --> 00:26:10.493
az der merder

00:26:10.493 --> 00:26:12.869
est shoyn on, est zikh shoyn on mit di blutn,

00:26:16.031 --> 00:26:17.021
ershte

00:26:18.545 --> 00:26:22.657
hobn zey, flegn zey nokh in grub dershisn andere, ⟨me flegt zikh nokh gelernt⟩.

00:26:22.916 --> 00:26:27.602
un oyf dem flegt zi shoyn nit azoy reagirn oyfn gantse mayse, UNK aranygefaln, arayngefaln,

00:26:28.181 --> 00:26:29.644
a lebedike, lebedike,

00:26:31.539 --> 00:26:32.625
un zey hobn shoyn

00:26:32.625 --> 00:26:34.284
UNK reagirt vayl UNK

00:26:34.357 --> 00:26:35.803
⟨dos mener⟩ iz geven ales shiker.

00:26:36.163 --> 00:26:41.299
UNK ikh veys nit vi in andere shtetlekh iz geven dort.

00:26:41.343 --> 00:26:43.531
maystns UNK half UNK oyf der erd.

00:26:44.583 --> 00:26:48.897
UNK me hot nokh gekent merer dort zayn UNK.

00:26:48.127 --> 00:26:50.011
iz ir zayt arayngefalm in grub?

00:26:53.156 --> 00:26:56.559
ikh bin in grub nit arayngefaln, vayl shisn

00:26:57.746 --> 00:26:59.675
iz mit di beymer forgeshtelt,

00:26:59.720 --> 00:27:01.098
hot zikh mir arayngegebn

00:27:01.678 --> 00:27:06.549
az ikh hob mir gezen, ikh ikh gedenk UNK nor ikh bin arayn in vald un antlofn.

00:27:06.673 --> 00:27:08.220
un me hot ir glaykh geshosn.

00:27:08.208 --> 00:27:09.049
geshosn.

00:27:09.049 --> 00:27:12.624
zey hobn dokh nit ge- zey hobn dokh nit gevust az ikh bin geranyet, az ikh bin farvundet.

00:27:11.347 --> 00:27:12.624
farvundet.

00:27:13.592 --> 00:27:15.308
ah, me hot aykh geshosn,

00:27:14.469 --> 00:27:18.446
zey flegn shisn un flegn zikh shoyn umdreyen, un azoy vet nit visn,

00:27:17.962 --> 00:27:20.842
ah un ir zent gelofn far dem vi me hot, vi me hot ongehoybn,

00:27:20.392 --> 00:27:24.234
nu, me hot ongefangen shisn zenen shoyn gelegn in gruber a sakh mentshn geshosn.

00:27:25.067 --> 00:27:26.867
un dan, un dan zayt ir gelofn.

00:27:26.467 --> 00:27:31.321
gelofn. un vu hob ikh gekent loyfn? ikh bin antlofn fun vald bin ikh arayngefaln

00:27:32.711 --> 00:27:34.292
bay maynem a

00:27:34.803 --> 00:27:38.949
nu a litvak, a nu a

00:27:39.123 --> 00:27:40.808
vi me zogt a UNK.

00:27:40.153 --> 00:27:41.160
a shokhn.

00:27:40.808 --> 00:27:42.392
a shokhn UNK.

00:27:41.418 --> 00:27:44.011
er iz geven, er iz ver, natsyonalitet?

00:27:43.882 --> 00:27:45.041
a litviner.

00:27:46.042 --> 00:27:49.496
mit zayn yingl fleg ikh geyn in klas, mir flegn zikh oyf im

00:27:49.755 --> 00:27:51.136
oyf UNK forn,

00:27:51.003 --> 00:27:52.432
khavern zikh.

00:27:51.667 --> 00:27:53.073
khavern zikh, zeyer.

00:27:53.366 --> 00:27:55.082
mir hobn gehat eygene vaser,

00:27:55.745 --> 00:27:57.056
flegn hodeven karpn.

00:27:59.610 --> 00:28:02.237
un zey, der litviner, hot gelebt nit vayt,

00:28:02.394 --> 00:28:04.313
zey hobn uNK fun di vasern UNK.

00:28:06.292 --> 00:28:08.041
flegn di brider mir betn,

00:28:08.148 --> 00:28:09.594
er iz geven zeyer a feiker,

00:28:09.954 --> 00:28:12.007
der der litviner, dem dem UNK,

00:28:12.148 --> 00:28:13.813
az mir flegn darfn geyn

00:28:14.460 --> 00:28:16.074
di esn likvidirn

00:28:16.569 --> 00:28:17.930
fun di ⟨vilde huntlekh⟩,

00:28:18.746 --> 00:28:20.732
vayl zey flegn oyskhapn di fish,

00:28:21.969 --> 00:28:23.718
muz men dokh in friling araynlozn kleynike,

00:28:24.483 --> 00:28:25.777
in zumer flegn zey oysvaksn.

00:28:26.795 --> 00:28:28.966
nu, se, dos iz amolike lebn gevezn azan.

00:28:30.018 --> 00:28:33.252
mir flegn in di velder klaybn nis, yagdes, shvemlekh,

00:28:34.878 --> 00:28:35.902
vi amolike nokh.

00:28:36.735 --> 00:28:40.037
nu, ikh bin geven a yungatsh.

00:28:41.021 --> 00:28:42.315
vos iz a yungatsh?

00:28:43.215 --> 00:28:45.858
mir flegn raysn

00:28:45.932 --> 00:28:48.896
