00:28:49.121 --> 00:28:49.877
un ikh,

00:28:49.880 --> 00:28:54.093
in di UNK hot zikh mir arayngegebn aza min dreystkeyt,

00:28:55.905 --> 00:28:57.075
azane khevre,

00:28:57.075 --> 00:28:58.987
mayne brider, zenen heldn geven.

00:28:59.145 --> 00:29:01.114
un andere UNK andere.
